		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />On second thought, the fastener might be there, just not depicted in the texture on the disc. SSBM's Dixie Kong trophy is evidence of this hypothesis: her shirt is obviously a button-down, as it's tied in a knot at her navel, but the overlapped part is shown with a solid color texture to save loading time.
<br />
